{"tid":674713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳新訓強逼女員工舔胸「破冰」 阿里巴巴否認","createTime":"2018-05-23T03:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T03:50:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"86bf972318ffdce152baddd430967c06d3a9df19","tid":674713,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/110235_f147ea87a0ccd92c0ade864e491f0eea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F110235_f147ea87a0ccd92c0ade864e491f0eea.png&h=7540743d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國電商龍頭阿里巴巴近日被踢爆，員工內部新訓時強逼男女員工大玩情色破冰遊戲，男主管也趁機猛吃豆腐，追問「第一次是什麼時候？」、「喜歡什麼姿勢」等私人問題。阿里巴巴則回應，網路流傳的圖片中人並非阿里巴巴員工，對網友有損公司名義的行為，將保留法律追訴權。<br />\n綜合媒體報導，阿里巴巴先前屢傳性別歧視問題，近日在中國微博上，又爆出一批據稱是阿里巴巴在成都的部門，員工新訓時進行「破冰遊戲」的照片，有女員工被要求舔男員工的胸、男員工跪著吃女員工的香蕉，甚至男男接吻等動作，引起大批網友熱議。<br />\n網友提到「阿里巴巴這種企業文化真令人作嘔」、「應該是真的，前公司以前玩破冰就是跟阿里學的」。也有網友加碼提到，阿里巴巴新訓時男主管常追問女員工私人問題，認為阿里巴巴的產品消費女性、培訓猥褻新人，「中國的企業文化就是三個字：不要臉！」。<br />\n對此，阿里巴巴回應表示，近日網上流傳所謂「阿里內部培訓」的謠言，經查圖中所涉絕非阿里巴巴的員工，更與阿里巴巴的培訓毫無關係，望廣大網友周知明辨。並強調，「針對冒用阿里名義，以及損及阿里名譽的行為，保留訴諸法律的權利」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/110346_b4aa3f948ed76f11b46812bc0c71c19b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F110346_b4aa3f948ed76f11b46812bc0c71c19b.png&h=125f5f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2434287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2434287&d=9hIK144lkxzBKkv7H8CMvZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6113ed47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2434287&h=f6382e99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2434287</a>"},{"pid":"a2cb6e3b8aa8e2ca03ebf6f9f8a368b562dee9aa","tid":674713,"uid":54524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:06:00.000Z","msg":"入去做陪訓完就走，跟住重新入去再陪訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b443abafe7d5959c79d45b671af3120511d497a5","tid":674713,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好開放呀<br />\n果然係阿里巴巴"},{"pid":"d9ba5fa1a14f27a5fddf1215eb490dd8206b3622","tid":674713,"uid":33064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"Ocamp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b55df698da7b3034c579670150947451c20803","tid":674713,"uid":113178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:14:02.000Z","msg":"右上好慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要同男人玩淫賤遊戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c713b015b14461cdc235be98f6897b9e1bda9498","tid":674713,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:16:57.000Z","msg":"中國ocamp"},{"pid":"79ceb82bc32c8864fdb5ff57af427c28c1b1ba28","tid":674713,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:38:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55159a5957ce2243944b0db2e92e5e36401fea42","tid":674713,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"支囯興共享經濟, 阿里巴巴準備推共享雞"},{"pid":"82b0772cc436760b7d46b042fa93f63bc108b690","tid":674713,"uid":174767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"破冰點解唔係舔雪條?"},{"pid":"26757b7473347e314a5e95d1ba7be23a2d7b12f2","tid":674713,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"